---
/**
 * ai-agents · 0005 · Figure 8 — long-running task timeline with checkpoints, a
 * crash at step five, and resume from the last checkpoint. Verbatim from the
 * source HTML.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 620 192"
        role="img"
        aria-label="A long-running task timeline with checkpoints after steps, a crash at step five, and a resume from the last checkpoint rather than a restart"
    >
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text x="310" y="16" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#9c968a"
                >task runs for hours/days &#8212; across process restarts</text
            >
            <!-- timeline -->
            <line x1="30" y1="70" x2="595" y2="70" stroke="#d8d4c8" stroke-width="2"></line>
            <!-- steps -->
            <g>
                <circle cx="70" cy="70" r="15" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"></circle><text
                    x="70"
                    y="74"
                    text-anchor="middle"
                    font-size="9"
                    font-weight="700"
                    fill="#2f5d3a">S1</text
                >
                <circle cx="160" cy="70" r="15" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"></circle><text
                    x="160"
                    y="74"
                    text-anchor="middle"
                    font-size="9"
                    font-weight="700"
                    fill="#2f5d3a">S2</text
                >
                <circle cx="270" cy="70" r="15" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"></circle><text
                    x="270"
                    y="74"
                    text-anchor="middle"
                    font-size="9"
                    font-weight="700"
                    fill="#2f5d3a">S3</text
                >
                <circle cx="360" cy="70" r="15" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"></circle><text
                    x="360"
                    y="74"
                    text-anchor="middle"
                    font-size="9"
                    font-weight="700"
                    fill="#2f5d3a">S4</text
                >
                <circle cx="450" cy="70" r="15" fill="#f7ecea" stroke="#9a2417"></circle><text
                    x="450"
                    y="74"
                    text-anchor="middle"
                    font-size="9"
                    font-weight="700"
                    fill="#9a2417">S5</text
                >
                <circle cx="540" cy="70" r="15" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"></circle><text
                    x="540"
                    y="74"
                    text-anchor="middle"
                    font-size="9"
                    font-weight="700"
                    fill="#6b675f">S6</text
                >
            </g>
            <!-- checkpoints -->
            <line
                x1="205"
                y1="70"
                x2="205"
                y2="104"
                stroke="#1f77d0"
                stroke-width="1.3"
                stroke-dasharray="3 2"></line>
            <rect x="183" y="104" width="44" height="18" rx="4" fill="#eef3fb" stroke="#1f77d0"
            ></rect><text x="205" y="117" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" fill="#1f77d0"
                >&#128190; ckpt</text
            >
            <line
                x1="405"
                y1="70"
                x2="405"
                y2="104"
                stroke="#1f77d0"
                stroke-width="1.3"
                stroke-dasharray="3 2"></line>
            <rect x="383" y="104" width="44" height="18" rx="4" fill="#eef3fb" stroke="#1f77d0"
            ></rect><text x="405" y="117" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" fill="#1f77d0"
                >&#128190; ckpt</text
            >
            <!-- crash -->
            <text x="450" y="44" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14">&#9889;</text>
            <text x="450" y="30" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" font-weight="700" fill="#9a2417"
                >CRASH</text
            >
            <!-- resume -->
            <path
                d="M405,122 L405,160 L450,160 L450,88"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                stroke-width="1.6"
                stroke-dasharray="5 3"
                marker-end="url(#arwG)"></path>
            <text
                x="300"
                y="176"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="9.5"
                font-weight="600"
                fill="#2f5d3a"
                >&#8635; resume from last checkpoint &mdash; replay, don't restart (so S1&ndash;S4
                don't re-run their side effects)</text
            >
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        Checkpoint after meaningful steps; on crash, resume from the last good checkpoint. For that
        to be safe, replayed steps must be idempotent &mdash; otherwise resume re-charges,
        re-emails, re-creates.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
